name: The Unnoticed Corner - an NFTNYC Story

metadata.name: The Witnesses
metadata.description:
Sitting on the train, the doors opened and these two Jehovah's Witnesses walked into the train and stood right next to where I was sitting. I turned my head, already having my camera in hand, and made this photograph. I showed them the photo and they were mind blown haha. I ended up getting their contact information and emailed them the photograph after I got back home.

Edition: 1 of 1

Collectors will receive a signed, 8x10'' Hahnemühle print, be entered into Tyler's collector community of photographers, and much more
